DISCIPLINARY CASES

2012-1181. Disciplinary Counsel v. Antony.

It is ordered by this- court, sua sponte, that John Peter Antony, Attorney Registration No. 0043520, last known business address in Highland Heights, Kentucky, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of September 6, 2012, to wit: faitee to file an affidavit of compliance on or before October 9, 2012.
